            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1717423092126-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Cut your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> lengthways, so that you end up with 3 strips per person</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1717423097051-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
